#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
CliShield — System-level ad blocker CLI tool.

Blocks ads, trackers, and telemetry across all applications by modifying
the system hosts file to redirect known ad-serving domains to 0.0.0.0.

Usage:
    sudo clishield activate       Enable ad blocking
    sudo clishield deactivate     Disable ad blocking
    sudo clishield --active       Shorthand for activate
    sudo clishield --inactive     Shorthand for deactivate
    clishield status              Show current status
    sudo clishield update         Refresh blocklists
    clishield stats               Show statistics

Requires root/admin privileges for activate, deactivate, and update commands.
Zero external dependencies — uses only Python 3 standard library.
"""

